Top 10! Merry Happy Everything Photo Navy Luxury Gold Foil Holiday Card – Hanukkah Cards This item is trending! Merry Happy Everything Photo Navy Luxury Gold Foil Holiday Card help you save during this period Merry Happy Everything Photo Navy Luxury Gold Foil Holiday Card You can read more about itAdd a touch of luxury to your holiday greetings with these real gold foil flat greeting cards featuring your photo and a navy blue Christmas tree and a matching Hanukkah Menorah. Add your photo to the upper left of the design where it will appear with rounded corners and a double border of gold foil. MERRY HAPPY EVERYTHING, also in gold foil, is balanced by the dark blue text to the right of your photo where you can add a Christmas or Hanukkah greeting along with your name and year. These personalized holiday greeting cards reverse to a solid medium blue with a thin pale blue border and space to add an additional greeting if you so choose. Designed as an option for interfaith Jewish and Christian couples and families who celebrate "Chrismukkah", these MERRY HAPPY EVERYTHING greeting cards with navy blue menorahs and trees are also perfect for Christmas or Hanukkah wishes for those who prefer a more all inclusive design.
